      • store

        List<String> store(String key,
                 List<StorageEntry> entries)

        Parameters:
        key - The directory key.
        entries - The file entries.
        Returns:
        All the keys that can be used to download the files later.

      • getDownloadFile

        File getDownloadFile(String downloadKey,
                   boolean compressed)
                     throws SynthesisException
        Retrieve the file for the download key.
        Parameters:
        downloadKey - The key returned from a store method call.
        compressed - Whether to compress the file of not.
        Returns:
        The file pointing to the relative file depending on the download key. Could be null if the file does not exist.
        Throws:
        SynthesisException - If the file could not be compressed/decompressed.

      • getDownloadFileStream

                                      throws SynthesisException

        Throws:
        SynthesisException - If the file could not be found
